/KA4. KEDUSHAT HAYOM / THE DAYÚS HOLINESS/XX/PR
You are one. Your name is one./PR
And who is like your people Israel,/PR
a unique people on the earth?/PR
/PR
Splendor of magnificence,/PR
the crown of divine help,/PR
a day of rest and holiness/PR
you gave to us, your people./PR
/PR
A restfulness of love and giving,/PR
a restfulness of truth and faith,/PR
a restfulness of peace and health,/PR
a restfulness of calm and trust,/PR
/PR
a perfect rest, one you take pleasure in--/PR
so may your children recognize and know:/PR
their rest has come from you,/PR
and for their rest they sanctify your name./PI/PR
